Entries.default: "Mighty Nemnok, we lay down our lives before your magnificence!"
"You are the keyhole, the stem of the rose, the jewel in the pommel!"
"You are the well and the bucket, the swaying of the corn, the curve of the sickle."
"You are where the path forks and meets again, the field and the wilderness."
"You are the branches and the roots, the fertile soil, the life that hides in water!"
"How delicious your embrace, mighty one! How ripe your pointed kiss!"
"That you should cast your gaze to such creatures as we, thigh-deep in our ignorance..."
"Ahem! Y- you are the songs of the night, the screams of the day!"
"Our supplication to you is total oh mightiest one, oh glorious Nemnok."
